Sentencas: The electrolyte materials Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.9 (SDC) and La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 (LSGM) are synthesized by glycine-nitrate processes, respectively.
Titulo: Performance of Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.9-La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 composite electrolytes for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Then SDC-LSGM composite electrolytes are prepared by mixing SDC and LSGM.
Titulo: Performance of Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.9-La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 composite electrolytes for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SDC and LSGM powders are mixed in the weight ratio of 95:5, 90:10 and 85:15 and named as SL9505, SL9010 and SL8515.
Titulo: Performance of Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.9-La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 composite electrolytes for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: SEM shows the grain size of SDC-LSGM composites increased distinctly.
Titulo: Performance of Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.9-La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 composite electrolytes for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical properties of SDC and SDC-LSGM composites are investigated.
Titulo: Performance of Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.9-La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 composite electrolytes for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The grain boundary resistance could be significantly decreased by small addition of LSGM.
Titulo: Performance of Ce0.85Sm0.15O1.9-La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 composite electrolytes for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The experimental results show that the SDC-LSGM composites exhibit excellent conductivity and could significantly enhance the fuel cell performances.
